1
00:00:21,480 --> 00:00:23,140
We can't be sure of our future.

2
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:25,920
But precisely because of so much uncertainty,

3
00:00:26,160 --> 00:00:28,400
it's all waiting for us to figure out.

4
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:29,480
This is a world

5
00:00:29,480 --> 00:00:31,480
defined by ourselves.

6
00:00:32,360 --> 00:00:33,820
That concludes my speech.

7
00:00:34,480 --> 00:00:35,240
Thank you.

8
00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:40,520
You must have a headache now.

9
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:42,040
Both are your students.

10
00:00:42,040 --> 00:00:42,960
Alas.

11
00:00:43,160 --> 00:00:44,600
As for Wen Lingli,

12
00:00:44,960 --> 00:00:46,760
she really didn't perform as well as Yin Zixi.

13
00:00:46,760 --> 00:00:48,760
But Yin Zixi's speech

14
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:50,360
doesn't match our theme.

15
00:00:57,280 --> 00:00:58,840
Great. Hold that pose.

16
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:02,200
Let's take another one from a different angle.

17
00:01:03,720 --> 00:01:05,080
Okay, Wen. You are good to go.

18
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:05,800
Oh.

19
00:01:14,039 --> 00:01:16,160
My body didn't lose control this time.

20
00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:19,690
Does it mean I won't lose control if I act according to the diary?

21
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:22,760
Hey.

22
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:25,080
The teacher letting both of you get selected

23
00:01:25,080 --> 00:01:26,320
is really amazing.

24
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:27,640
Where is Chen?

25
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:30,840
He probably went to change clothes.

26
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:50,759
Why are you walking so slowly?

27
00:01:50,759 --> 00:01:51,479
Oh.

28
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:54,520
Alright.

29
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:55,450
Just relax a bit.

30
00:01:55,479 --> 00:01:57,340
Did you talk to the photographer?

31
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:59,560
Don't worry, I've got this.

32
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:01,560
Get closer, face to face.

33
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:06,650
What's going on?

34
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,520
Maybe they're taking turns.

35
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:09,320
Wait a minute.

36
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:11,290
Hey, put your arm around her waist.

37
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:12,960
Hey, that's not right.

38
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:15,440
The guy should put his arm around the girl's waist.

39
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:16,320
Ah.

40
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:18,640
Liang Chen, your clothes are crooked.

41
00:02:18,640 --> 00:02:19,900
Let me fix them for you.

42
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:23,300
Am I the photographer, or are you?

43
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:25,160
Go away. I can see for myself.

44
00:02:30,079 --> 00:02:31,920
You two, face to face first.

45
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:32,920
Okay.

46
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,240
Don't be shy.

47
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:36,079
Both of you, reach out your hands

48
00:02:36,079 --> 00:02:37,160
toward each other.

49
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,160
Don't be shy.

50
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,480
Take the initiative.

51
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:45,880
I told you to take couple photos before,

52
00:02:46,640 --> 00:02:48,160
but not of these two.

53
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:49,960
Oh.

54
00:02:51,079 --> 00:02:51,840
Got it.

55
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,980
Yin, your photos are done.

56
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:56,160
Ah, okay.

57
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:58,040
I'll get going then. Thank you.

58
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:58,760
Let me walk you back.

59
00:02:58,760 --> 00:02:59,520
Hey, boss,

60
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:01,640
you still have two more photos to take.

61
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:02,760
Me? Do I have more?

62
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:04,520
Yes, boss. Wait a moment.

63
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:05,180
Come on,

64
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,240
put your arm around his waist.

65
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,400
Hey, face to face.

66
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:08,200
Hey.

67
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:10,040
Great. Hold that pose.

68
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:21,680
No, what are you talking about?

69
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,880
That's not right. No.

70
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:30,880
Dad, don't you think your daughter

71
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,680
has a great talent for business?

72
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:35,640
Just lend me some money to start a business.

73
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:37,079
Those projects you mentioned,

74
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:38,800
if I had the money, I would have invested in them long ago.

75
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,079
I don't need you to teach me.

76
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:40,720
Oh.

77
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:42,520
You've already missed out on investing in properties,

78
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:44,520
so you can't miss out on your daughter now.

79
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,600
I have nothing.

80
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,160
Let alone 5000, I don't even have 500.

81
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:48,440
Go ask your mom, sweetie.

82
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:49,760
Ugh, there's no way my mom would agree.

83
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:50,880
Just focus on your studies.

84
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:51,920
Hey, Dad.

85
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:56,240
A family of cheapskates.

86
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,040
Why couldn't I

87
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:03,560
memorize a few more lottery numbers?

88
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,840
Wow, who are you?

89
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:13,280
Since you asked so sincerely,

90
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:15,960
I will kindly tell you.

91
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,320
I am

92
00:04:17,320 --> 00:04:18,079
Yin Zixi.

93
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,000
Yeah.

94
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:21,600
Are you rich now?

95
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:23,920
Don't ask.

96
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:26,200
I finally got the startup fund,

97
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:28,010
but we have to split it equally.

98
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,920
At least you won.

99
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,760
Is it enough for your livestream?

100
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:33,000
It was supposed to be enough.

101
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,600
Now it's just a little short.

102
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:39,640
Just a tiny bit short.

103
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:41,520
Yang Qian, I want...

104
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:42,760
I don't have any.

105
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:47,880
Yang Qian, just invest a little bit.

106
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:49,159
Not a single bit.

107
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:51,960
You should shift your investment focus.

108
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,640
Let's not look too far ahead.

109
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:58,159
I still prefer familiar investors.

110
00:04:58,159 --> 00:05:00,560
Then you can only look for angel investors.

111
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:01,640
Angel Yang.

112
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:02,900
Hey, stop right there.

113
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:05,440
Let me think.

114
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:08,240
It seems you can borrow money from the student council.

115
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,320
The student council?

116
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:09,880
Yeah.

117
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:12,100
Starting from the previous term,

118
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:15,120
the student council president back then was very rich.

119
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,560
If a student had financial difficulties,

120
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:18,890
he would transfer cash to them on the spot.

121
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:20,400
They didn't even have to write an IOU.

122
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:22,080
That's not an investor.

123
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,200
That's a saint.

124
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,520
Have you figured out how to borrow money?

125
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:28,200
First, I'll submit my business plan.

126
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:32,720
You don't study hard, but think about making money.

127
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,159
Hey,

128
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:34,120
my book!

129
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,720
Mr. Wang is busy today.

130
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:40,080
I'm proctoring for him.

131
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,960
The exam lasts 90 minutes.

132
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,440
It starts now.

133
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:45,960
These are the exam papers.

134
00:05:46,280 --> 00:05:47,280
Before you start,

135
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:50,720
fill in your name, student ID, and class.

136
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:53,360
Everyone must follow the exam rules.

137
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,400
No whispering

138
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:56,080
or any form of cheating.

139
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,580
I will be watching you.

140
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:07,840
Ah, finally done.

141
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:17,640
Pens down, hand in your papers.

142
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:19,840
Senior, don't we have ten more minutes?

143
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,240
Don't waste my time.

144
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:22,580
You didn't study hard,

145
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,440
so ten extra minutes

146
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,940
won't help you finish.

147
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,400
Hand in your papers.

148
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:31,320
The exam time is 90 minutes.

149
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:33,040
Why collect them early?

150
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,480
Stop whining.

151
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:37,280
This is unfair to my classmates.

152
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,000
I'm the proctor.

153
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:41,120
I decide when you hand in the papers.

154
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:43,360
Why are you students so difficult?

155
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:46,560
Senior.

156
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:48,700
Just say what you want.

157
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:49,720
Don't point at others.

158
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,760
What do you mean?

159
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,240
Playing the hero?

160
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,000
Look at your own paper.

161
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:58,200
It's completely blank.

162
00:06:58,200 --> 00:07:00,600
How dare you mind other people's business?

163
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,450
It was my negligence this time.

164
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:04,200
I will definitely pass the makeup exam.

165
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:06,880
But you ignored the exam rules,

166
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,640
failed the teacher's trust,

167
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:11,080
and treated us unjustly and unfairly.

168
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:33,640
This apology,

169
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:35,490
I hope you can make up for it.

170
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:48,880
I'm sorry.

171
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:54,960
The proctor went too far.

172
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:57,440
I can't believe they collected the papers ten minutes early.

173
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:58,200
Thanks.

174
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:21,370
How's your revision going?

175
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,760
I gave up.

176
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:23,960
Let it be.

177
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,600
Ah.

178
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:26,770
Then what about your startup fund?

179
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:28,860
What's wrong with my fund?

180
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:30,760
I heard the senior proctor

181
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:32,720
complained about you to the teacher.

182
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:34,640
So the school put your role as the image ambassador

183
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:35,280
on hold.

184
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:35,960
What?

185
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:38,440
It's unfair of the school to do this.

186
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,440
Unjust and unrighteous.

187
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,120
Yeah.

188
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:42,970
The senior was clearly in the wrong first.

189
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:45,600
But there's good news.

190
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,080
Tell me.

191
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:49,040
Wen Lingli didn't pass the exam either.

192
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:50,040
Mr. Wang said

193
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:51,280
you two will have a make-up exam.

194
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:53,610
Whoever passes gets to be the ambassador.

195
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:55,120
That means

196
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,800
I don't have to split my fund.

197
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:00,480
Got it.

198
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:01,360
By the way.

199
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:02,840
There's also bad news.

200
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:04,000
Another one?

201
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,800
The make-up exam is set for the 16th,

202
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:06,280
which is

203
00:09:06,880 --> 00:09:07,680
in three days.

204
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:08,840
Three days?

205
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:14,560
It seems only one person can help you.

206
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:17,680
I heard that person took a leave of absence for half a year.

207
00:09:17,680 --> 00:09:20,720
After returning, he is still the top student in the college.

208
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:23,160
With his tutoring, there will definitely be no problem.

209
00:09:23,160 --> 00:09:24,560
He is that living Buddha,

210
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:26,680
the former president of the Student Union,

211
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:27,400
An Yufan.

212
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:30,120
Even if he is a living Buddha,

213
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:32,600
he wouldn't tutor me for no reason, right?

214
00:09:33,520 --> 00:09:34,400
Sigh.

215
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:55,400
Casting Director Xi Chongjing.

216
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:57,360
Props Assistant Li Kunxiao.

217
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:59,280
Location Vehicle Yi Mingle.

218
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:01,160
Yitong.
